{
  "id": "69a956597f77ea6cdc5029e5",
  "title": "黒歴史との向き合い方",
  "created": 1772705399,
  "updated": 1772744892,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a956597f77ea6cdc5029e5",
      "text": "黒歴史との向き合い方",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705399,
      "updated": 1772705399
    },
    {
      "id": "69a957710000000000fad3d7",
      "text": "[黒歴史]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705649,
      "updated": 1772705653
    },
    {
      "id": "69a957720000000000fad3d8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705651,
      "updated": 1772705651
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956960000000000fad3d2",
      "text": "[ふーことましろとひよりの会話]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705430,
      "updated": 1772705436
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956820000000000fad3d1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705410,
      "updated": 1772705410
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956770000000000fad335",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705399,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad336",
      "text": "「はいどーも！放課後トークタイム〜。今日のテーマは……ドン！[**** 『黒歴史との向き合い方』]でーす。いやーこれ、みんな1個はあるっしょ？中二ポエムとか、SNSの痛い投稿とか。思い出すと“[うわあああ]”ってなるやつ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705730
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad337",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad338",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad339",
      "text": "「ふふ、ありますよね。思い出しただけで顔が熱くなるような出来事。そういう経験って、誰にでもあると思うんです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad33a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad33b",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad33c",
      "text": "「統計的にも、その認識は妥当。思春期は自己形成の途中だから、過去の行動を“痛い”と再評価する現象はかなり一般的」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad33d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad33e",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad33f",
      "text": "「急に論文っぽくなったｗ でもつまり、“黒歴史あるのは普通”ってことだよね？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad340",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad341",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad342",
      "text": "「要約するとそう」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad343",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad344",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad345",
      "text": "「それを聞くと少し安心しますね。自分だけじゃないんだ、って」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad346",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad347",
      "text": "[hr.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad348",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad349",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad34a",
      "text": "「でもさー、問題はここからなんよ。黒歴史って、たまに[** 夜に急にフラッシュバック]して“うわああああ”ってなるじゃん。あれどうすればいいの？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad34b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad34c",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad34d",
      "text": "「対処法はいくつかある。まず基本は[** 時間距離を置いて再解釈すること]」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad34e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad34f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad350",
      "text": "「お、出た専門ワード。翻訳お願いしまーす」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad351",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad352",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad353",
      "text": "「簡単に言うと、[** “今の自分の目線で過去を見直す]”」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad354",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad355",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad356",
      "text": "「たしかに、当時は一生懸命だったんですよね。その時の自分なりに」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad357",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad358",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad359",
      "text": "「そう。過去の自分は、その時点の知識と経験で最善を選んでいる可能性が高い」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad35a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad35b",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad35c",
      "text": "「つまり、“当時の自分、まあしゃーない”ってやつ？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad35d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad35e",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad35f",
      "text": "「かなり近い」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad360",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad361",
      "text": "[hr.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad362",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad363",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad364",
      "text": "「わたしは、黒歴史を思い出したときは“よく頑張ってたね”って心の中で声をかけるようにしてます」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad365",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad366",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad367",
      "text": "「え、やさし……聖母か？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad368",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad369",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad36a",
      "text": "「そんな大げさじゃないですよ。でも、自分を責めすぎるとつらくなりますから」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad36b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad36c",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad36d",
      "text": "「心理学でも、自分への過度な批判はストレス反応を強めると報告されている」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad36e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad36f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad370",
      "text": "「ましろ理論、エビデンス付きだった」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad371",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad372",
      "text": "[hr.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad373",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad374",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad375",
      "text": "「でもさ、逆パターンもあるよね。黒歴史を[** 完全封印]して“なかったこと”にするやつ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad376",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad377",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad378",
      "text": "「それは短期的には楽。ただし長期的には処理されない記憶として残りやすい」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad379",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad37a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad37b",
      "text": "「つまり、心のゴミ箱に入れたつもりが、[** 実はデスクトップに残ってるショートカット]みたいな？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad37c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad37d",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad37e",
      "text": "「その比喩は正確」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad37f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad380",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad381",
      "text": "「ふふ、わかりやすいですね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad382",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad383",
      "text": "[hr.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad384",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad385",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad386",
      "text": "「じゃあさ、黒歴史って[** 消すよりネタ化]したほうがいいのかな？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad387",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad388",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad389",
      "text": "「それは有効な戦略の一つ。自分の失敗をユーモアとして再構築する」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad38a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad38b",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad38c",
      "text": "「笑いに変えられると、少し軽くなりますよね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad38d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad38e",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad38f",
      "text": "「わかる〜。“昔こんな痛いことしてたｗ”って言えると、もう勝ち感ある」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad390",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad391",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad392",
      "text": "「それは[** 認知の再フレーム化]」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad393",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad394",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad395",
      "text": "「翻訳！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad396",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad397",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad398",
      "text": "「[** 見方を変える]」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad399",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad39a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad39b",
      "text": "「OK理解した」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad39c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad39d",
      "text": "[hr.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad39e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad39f",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3a0",
      "text": "「でも、無理に笑いにしなくてもいいと思うんです。まだ痛い思い出のときもありますし」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3a1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3a2",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3a3",
      "text": "「同意。処理の速度は人によって違う」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3a4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3a5",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3a6",
      "text": "「たしかに。黒歴史にも[** 熟成期間]あるよね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3a7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3a8",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3a9",
      "text": "「ワインみたいですね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3aa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3ab",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3ac",
      "text": "「比喩としては悪くない」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3ad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3ae",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3af",
      "text": "「まとめるとさー、今日のポイントはこんな感じ？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3b0",
      "text": " 1. 黒歴史は[** みんなあるので安心]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3b1",
      "text": " 2. 当時の自分は[** その時なりにベスト]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3b2",
      "text": " 3. 見方を変えると[** ネタや学びになる]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3b3",
      "text": " 4. 無理に忘れなくてもOK",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3b4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3b5",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3b6",
      "text": "「とてもいいまとめだと思います」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3b7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3b8",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3b9",
      "text": "「要点は押さえている」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3ba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3bb",
      "text": "[hr.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3bc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3bd",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3be",
      "text": "「よし！じゃ最後に一言ずつ。黒歴史に悩んでる人へメッセージ！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3bf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3c0",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3c1",
      "text": "「もし過去の自分を思い出して恥ずかしくなったら、それはきっと[** 今の自分が成長している証拠]だと思います。どうか優しくしてあげてくださいね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3c2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3c3",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3c4",
      "text": "「過去の行動を客観的に見られるのは、認知が更新された証拠。つまり、[** アップデート済み]ということ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3c5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3c6",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3c7",
      "text": "「いいこと言うじゃん。じゃあ私はこれで締めるね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3c8",
      "text": "黒歴史はね……[** [人生のバグ]じゃなくてアップデートログ]です。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772744892
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3c9",
      "text": "以上、ふーこでした！解散！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3ca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3cb",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3cc",
      "text": "「ふふ、おつかれさまでした」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3cd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3ce",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3cf",
      "text": "「終了」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    },
    {
      "id": "69a956780000000000fad3d0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772705400,
      "updated": 1772705400
    }
  ]
}